dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Adams_Addresss_2018.gdb.[Adams County Address Points - Attribute table is formatted for use by the Spillman emergency dispatch system and the ESRI Alphanumeric geocoder. Metadata is minimal, only the attribute descriptions have been recorded.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Adams County Register of Deeds/ Land Records
